sequenceDiagram
  participant UI as Models Section (App.tsx)
  participant Cmd as Tauri Commands
  participant Mgr as ModelDownloadManager
  participant Hub as hf_hub API
  participant Cache as Local HF Cache
  participant Bus as Event Bus

  UI->>Cmd: start_model_download(model_key)
  Cmd->>Mgr: queue model + maybe start next
  Mgr->>Bus: emit model-download-state-changed
  Bus-->>UI: queued/downloading status

  loop For each required file
    Mgr->>Cache: check cached artifact
    alt Missing in cache
      Mgr->>Hub: download_with_progress(file)
      Hub-->>Mgr: progress callbacks
      Mgr->>Bus: throttled progress updates (200ms)
      Bus-->>UI: downloaded bytes + speed
    else Present in cache
      Mgr->>Mgr: count file as completed
    end
  end

  alt Download succeeds and files verified
    Mgr->>Mgr: set status = ready
  else Download fails or canceled
    Mgr->>Mgr: set status = failed/canceled
  end

  Mgr->>Bus: emit final snapshot
  Bus-->>UI: refresh model cards and queue
